thread.title: BRIEF-Xiamen Unigroup Xue expects to return profitable in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Xiamen Unigroup Xue expects to return profitable in FY 2017

organizations.name: reuters) - xiamen unigroup xue co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Xiamen Unigroup Xue Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to be 16 million yuan to 24 million yuan
* Says the net loss of FY 2016 was 98.7 million yuan
* Comments that inclusion of new companies and increased educational training income as main reasons for the forecast
